        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Virtual Currency Tax Fairness Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill excludes from gross income, for income tax purposes, up to $200 of gain from the disposition of virtual currency in a personal transaction. The bill defines<i> virtual currency</i> as a digital representation of value that is used as a medium of exchange and is not otherwise currency.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
